comments:
Abolished 1.4.1932 and divided between the parishes of Horndean, 
    Rowlands Castle and Havant. See also Table 2, notes (b) and (c).

Abolished 1.4.1932 and divided between the parishes of Havant and 
    Horndean. See also Table 2, note (b).

Abolished 1.4.1932 and added to the parish of Clanfield and 
    Rowlands Castle. See also Table 2, note (c).

Created 1.4.1932 out of the parishes of Catherington and Blendworth. 
    See also Table 2, note (c).

Abolished 1.4.1932 and added to the parish of Rowlands Castle. 
    See also Table 2, note (c).

That part which until 1.4.1932 formed the parish of Idsworth 
    and parts of the parishes of Blendworth and Chalton. See also Table 2, note 
    (c).

Abolished 1.4.1932 and divided between the parishes of Havant and 
    Southwick & Widley. See also Table 2, notes (a) and (b).
